      • getId

        public int getId()
        Returns the int identifier of the type. Note: This is only used for getting the int representation of the type for DataServerMessage, since that class needs to manually encode all messages. DataServerMessage and this method should no longer be needed when the client is converted to use Netty.
        Returns:
        the int id of the type
